Yesterday I sent you by Express the MS I told you about. I need hardly remind you that I am submitting it to S. & S. on a highly confidential basis.





Sincerely yours

Vladimir Nabokov





TO: JAMES LAUGHLIN

CC, 1 p.





General Delivery

Taos, N.M.

July 4, 1954

Dear Mr. Laughlin,

